  "prompt": "Which is the best cream available in india with Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, Ester C and Dermaxyl?",
  "response": "In India, one of the best creams that contains Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, Ester C, and Dermaxyl is the \"Cosmoderm's Vitamin C Ester, Kojic Acid & Alpha Arbutin Cream with Dermaxyl.\" This cream is formulated to address skin concerns like hyperpigmentation, dark spots, and uneven skin tone, while also providing anti-aging benefits.\n\nHere's a brief overview of the key ingredients and their benefits:\n\n1. **Kojic Acid**: Helps in reducing hyperpigmentation and lightening skin tone by inhibiting melanin production.\n2. **Alpha Arbutin**: Another potent skin lightening agent that works by reducing melanin synthesis.\n3. **Ester C (Vitamin C Ester)**: A stable form of Vitamin C that helps in brightening the skin, boosting collagen production, and providing antioxidant protection.\n4. **Dermaxyl**: A peptide that helps in improving skin texture and reducing the appearance of wrinkles and fine lines.\n\nYou can find this product on various online platforms like Amazon, Nykaa, or the official Cosmoderm website. Always perform a patch test before using any new skincare product and consult with a dermatologist if you have specific skin concerns or conditions.",
